comments.body:
@csutcliff  To upgrade custom firmware you need to put 
6565-0391-10083001-tuya_thermostat_zrd.zigbee  to the corresponding folder (e.g. images in your case) and add it to local_ota file:

```json
{
        "url": "images/6565-0391-10083001-tuya_thermostat_zrd.zigbee"
}
```

d3a3 file is used for the initial flashing only. Now for upgraded devices the manufacturer code is 6565
